<HEAD>One Month After Derailment, Neighbors Fear Physical, Financial Ruin</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By LEE SIEGEL</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SAN BERNARDINO, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
